- -Isn't it, dear?

49:47.985 --> 49:48.985
Don't be stupid!

49:49.028 --> 49:53.115
There are no wolves in Japan anymore.
That's a Shepherd mixed with something else.

49:53.324 --> 49:56.035
Right, Hana? Am I right? Am I right?

49:56.243 --> 49:57.870
Oh? The dog's gone.

49:58.078 --> 49:59.997
Hello, Mrs. Nirasaki!

50:00.206 --> 50:02.875
Oh hello, yuki. Aren't you friendly today.

50:03.083 --> 50:05.753
Oh, you and the dog have matching clothes!

50:05.961 --> 50:08.214
That's cute.

50:08.422 --> 50:11.675
Yu... yuki...

50:15.763 --> 50:17.640
What's wrong, Hana?

50:39.161 --> 50:40.788
Hello?

50:42.289 --> 50:43.958
Hello!

50:50.130 --> 50:53.092
