51:05.229 --> 51:06.397
The boar, that bastard...

51:06.605 --> 51:08.941
Oh, thank you for bringing this.

51:09.149 --> 51:12.486
It came and dug everything up
without making a sound.

51:12.695 --> 51:15.698
It came all the way down
to sakai's fields this year.

51:15.906 --> 51:18.158
Here, take this in return.
Watch out, it's heavy.

51:18.367 --> 51:21.745
The only fields with
no animal damage are yours, Hana.

51:21.954 --> 51:24.224
It's strange, even though
you're so deep in the mountains.

51:24.248 --> 51:25.791
Do you have some kind of trick?

51:26.000 --> 51:27.251
No, I don't...

51:27.459 --> 51:29.253
Everyone wants to know how you did it.

51:29.461 --> 51:30.796
What's a trick?

51:31.005 --> 51:32.172
I need to pee!

51:32.381 --> 51:35.009
Yuki's a lively child, isn't she?

51:35.926 --> 51:36.927
Could it be...?

51:37.136 --> 51:38.262
What is it?

51:38.470 --> 51:40.889
Oh, no, never mind.

51:41.098 --> 51:43.309
Wow, thank you very much.

51:43.517 --> 51:44.018
Don't mention it.

51:44.226 --> 51:45.436
Thanks for the potatoes.

51:45.644 --> 51:47.084
It's been a while since we had eggs.

51:47.146 --> 51:48.397
I'm glad to help.

51:48.606 --> 51:50.441
Let me know when you run out!

51:50.649 --> 51:53.694
Oh my, isn't that cute!

51:55.362 --> 51:56.363
What?

51:56.572 --> 51:57.323
Ready, lift.

51:57.531 --> 51:59.658
Oh, you don't have to give us
something so big...

51:59.867 --> 52:01.535
Don't worry about it.

52:01.744 --> 52:03.454
It was just sitting in the storage shed.

52:03.662 --> 52:04.788
But...

52:04.997 --> 52:08.584
Please take it. If we bring it
back, gramps'll get mad at us.

52:08.792 --> 52:10.002
Grandpa nirasaki?

52:10.210 --> 52:12.421
He's always talking about you, Hana.

52:12.630 --> 52:13.690
Because he's fallen for her.

52:13.714 --> 52:15.382
Come on, he's already ninety.

52:15.591 --> 52:18.636
But he even told everyone
to help her and everything.

52:18.844 --> 52:21.430
Idiot! He said not to say anything
about that, remember?!

52:22.640 --> 52:24.933
So that's what it was...?

52:38.864 --> 52:43.869
I finally understand
why I needed a bigger field.

52:48.666 --> 52:49.917
I don't like it.

52:50.125 --> 52:51.168
What?

52:51.377 --> 52:54.338
