53:03.681 --> 53:06.058
What's so funny?

53:15.442 --> 53:20.322
We moved here trying
to get away from prying eyes...

53:20.531 --> 53:24.284
When did we end up in the care
of the people from the village?

53:26.286 --> 53:32.209
It was hard at first,
but I think we'll do fine here.

53:41.093 --> 53:43.053
Wow, look at that!

