57:33.033 --> 57:35.369
Open your eyes! Ame!

57:35.577 --> 57:37.079
Open your eyes!

57:37.287 --> 57:41.583
Ame, ame, ame...

57:41.792 --> 57:46.588
Open your eyes...

57:47.673 --> 57:50.092
Mommy... that's... too tight...

57:50.300 --> 57:51.760
Ame!!

57:51.969 --> 57:53.428
You know what?

57:53.637 --> 57:56.348
I found a crested kingfisher.

57:56.556 --> 58:03.313
It was a really nice-looking bird.
I felt like even I could catch it today.

58:03.522 --> 58:07.401
It was completely different
from how it usually feels.

58:07.609 --> 58:12.531
I wasn't scared. Suddenly,
I felt like I could do anything.

58:12.739 --> 58:14.658
So then, I...

58:16.702 --> 58:18.620
Why are you crying?

58:19.746 --> 58:22.457
What are we doing here?

58:27.671 --> 58:32.551
Mother said later that she had
never been more frightened in her life.

58:33.719 --> 58:39.307
After that incident, ame seemed
like a completely different person.

