1:51:28.849 --> 1:51:32.269
“Ame“ “the forest is alive“

1:51:49.620 --> 1:51:56.335
"I hope to meet you soon, “

1:51:56.543 --> 1:52:03.467
I always prayed as I rubbed my belly

1:52:03.675 --> 1:52:11.675
What will you look like?

1:52:16.772 --> 1:52:24.772
What will you sound like?

1:52:31.995 --> 1:52:38.043
Isee my reflection in your big eyes

1:52:38.252 --> 1:52:44.800
as teardrops spill onto your cheeks

1:52:45.008 --> 1:52:53.008
Come here, the food's ready!

1:52:57.813 --> 1:53:05.813
Come on, let's go for a walk!

1:53:11.493 --> 1:53:17.833
Your eyes swollen, you sit
with your arms around your knees

1:53:18.041 --> 1:53:24.506
tell me why you're
crying, tell me everything

1:53:24.715 --> 1:53:30.721
don't worry, I'm not going anywhere

1:53:30.929 --> 1:53:37.185
no matter what happens, we'll be together

1:53:37.394 --> 1:53:43.483
I love your smiling face

1:53:43.692 --> 1:53:49.865
it makes me feel better, even when I'm down

1:53:50.073 --> 1:53:58.073
Come here, let's sing!

1:54:02.210 --> 1:54:10.210
Come on,
let's raise our voices together!

1:54:14.848 --> 1:54:22.848
I want you to grow up brightly and freely

1:54:28.779 --> 1:54:34.326
Running in the snow, counting clouds

1:54:34.534 --> 1:54:40.207
playing in the rain,
being blown by the wind

1:54:40.415 --> 1:54:45.879
buried under flowers, playing grass kazoos

1:54:46.088 --> 1:54:51.843
on four feet, on two feet

1:54:52.052 --> 1:54:54.805
a new morning

1:54:55.013 --> 1:54:57.516
a new wind

1:54:57.724 --> 1:55:03.271
preparedjust for you

1:55:03.480 --> 1:55:06.024
a new morning

1:55:06.233 --> 1:55:08.860
a new light

1:55:09.069 --> 1:55:14.491
the world is yours for the taking

1:55:14.699 --> 1:55:17.327
a new morning

1:55:17.536 --> 1:55:20.205
a new rainbow

1:55:20.414 --> 1:55:25.919
the world is full of mystery

1:55:26.128 --> 1:55:34.128
choosing one of two paths,
eyes fixed on a point far away

1:55:45.147 --> 1:55:53.147
Is there nothing else I can do for you?

1:56:00.412 --> 1:56:08.412
Whenever you decide to leave,
I will see you off with a smile

1:56:18.513 --> 1:56:26.513
But I'll still be a little sad

1:56:30.233 --> 1:56:38.233
Please, live a good life
